#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/TG/tg_12f.rst:8
#: a733971203fb43deb0ef2862fa82f56c
msgid ""
"TG-12F模块采用平头哥TG7100C芯片，TG7100C 是智能新一代高集成 Wi-Fi 和 BLE 组合芯片。无线子系统包含 2.4G 射频"
"、Wi-Fi 802.11b/g/n 和 BLE 基带/MAC 设计。微控制器子系统包含一个低功耗 32 位 RISC "
"CPU、高速缓存和存储器。电源管理单元提供灵活的设置实现低功耗模式，并支持多种安全功能。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/TG/tg_12f.rst:10
#: 4f9d2f31ebc2436b9d46d78188280bbe
msgid "产品特性："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/TG/tg_12f.rst:12
#: d00028bbfa284d47962d432dd425c1ac
msgid "802.11b/g/n，Wi-Fi+BLE5.0 Combo，支持 STA，Soft AP 和 Sniffer模式"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/TG/tg_12f.rst:13
#: fe9db1302ddc449f8ac7a920832c7799
msgid "采用开源自主可控 RISC-V CPU，1～160MHz 可调，276KB SRAM"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/TG/tg_12f.rst:14
#: 0266c8bee2484bef9c4a369c77c945aa
msgid "超快连接：冷启动快连仅 70ms"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/TG/tg_12f.rst:15
#: 1cbfbbe39b2f4c56b1b9325b5ddc1953
msgid "超远距离：最大发射功率 21dBm，灵敏度-98dBm，多穿透一堵墙。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/TG/tg_12f.rst:16
#: c43a2f736c144b1b9011810cede2b4f5
msgid ""
"高安全性：支持安全启动、安全调试、AES 128/192/256 "
"加密引擎、WPA3、MD5、SHA-1/224/256、PKA（RSA/ECC）加密     引擎"
msgstr ""

